description: On December 18, 1999, during the intermission between sets of the Saxophone Summit Live at Birdland, the webcast on GMN, I interviewed Michael Brecker, Joe Lovano and Dave Liebman. We lost the intro, but here's what survived. Grover Washington, Jr. passed away the day before so my first question was about Grover.  Many thanks to Louis Gerrits for the color correction.
title: Interview with Michael Brecker, Joe Lovano, Dave Liebman - 12/18/99
fulltitle: Interview with Michael Brecker, Joe Lovano, Dave Liebman - 12/18/99
